sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway
    participant Sidecar as llm-d-routing-sidecar<br/>:8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller Pod<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>:8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2 Protocol)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port: host:port<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefill target host<br/>against InferencePool pod IPs
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed (or 403 Forbidden)

    Note over Sidecar: Construct prefill request:<br/>wrap body with kv_transfer_params<br/>set max_tokens=1, stream=false<br/>add remote_decode=true, engine_id

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Modified body with kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>Contains: block_ids, engine_id,<br/>host, port for KV transfer

    Note over Sidecar: Extract KV transfer params<br/>from prefill response.<br/>Construct decode request with<br/>remote_prefill=true + block/engine info

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Body with kv_transfer_params<br/>(remote_prefill=true)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Decode response (streamed)
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Passthrough (No Prefill Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port header)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Sidecar: No prefill header detected.<br/>Passthrough to local decoder.

    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward request as-is<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response (streamed)
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
